# .verible_verilog_lint
# SystemVerilog linter config for RV32I CPU project

-forbid_register   # No 'reg' keyword
+always_ff         # Require always_ff for sequential
+always_comb       # Require always_comb for combinational

+port_naming       # Flag ports that don't follow _i/_o/_n suffix convention

+signal_naming     # Enforce snake_case

+module_naming     # Enforce snake_case module names